## 7. Global Wave Resource Atlas

```elixir
atlas = EnergyX.Renewable.WaveTidalOTEC.wave_resource_atlas()
IO.puts("Global Wave Power Resource (kW/m of wavefront):")
atlas |> Enum.sort_by(fn {_,v} -> -v.typical_kw_m end) |> Enum.each(fn {region, data} ->
  IO.puts("  #{region}: #{data.typical_kw_m} kW/m typical (#{data.best_kw_m} kW/m peak)")
end)
```

